##? Post load function for zsh-history-substring-search plugin
# https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-history-substring-search

# Emacs
bind2maps emacs -- history-substring-search-up Up Ctrl+P
bind2maps emacs -- history-substring-search-down Down Ctrl+N

# Vi
bind2maps viins -- history-substring-search-up Up
bind2maps viins -- history-substring-search-down Down
bind2maps vicmd -- history-substring-search-up K
bind2maps vicmd -- history-substring-search-down J
